# Graphiti (Zep) Service

Temporal Knowledge Graph service powered by [Graphiti](https://github.com/getzep/graphiti).

## Configuration

This service is configured via environment variables in `docker-compose.yml`:

- `NEO4J_URI`: URI for Neo4j database (default: `bolt://neo4j:7687`)
- `NEO4J_PASSWORD`: Password for Neo4j authentication
- `GRAPHITI_DATABASE`: Name of the Neo4j database to use (default: `memory`)
- `OPENAI_API_KEY`: API key for LLM operations

## API

The service exposes a REST API at port `8000` (or configured port).

- `GET /healthz`: Health check endpoint
- `GET /`: Service status
